Package org.opengis.cite.iso19136.data

package org.opengis.cite.iso19136.data
Includes tests that apply to GML documents. A GML document has one of the following elements as its root element (4.1.35):
  • a GML feature (an element that substitutes for gml:AbstractFeature);
  • gml:Dictionary;
  • gml:TopoComplex;
See Also:
  • "ISO 19136, A.3: Abstract test suite for GML documents"

    org.opengis.cite.iso19136.recommendations
    Includes tests covering recommended constraints that need not be satisfied by a fully conforming IUT.
